205
00:09:58,138 --> 00:10:00,793
If You Hate It Here, If You
Think You'd Be So Much Happier

206
00:10:00,793 --> 00:10:03,703
Working For Wilhelmina, Go.
Is That
What You Want Me To Do?

207
